    <h1 class="post-title">Easy Japanese: At the Hotel / Ryokan</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--muted)">Essential phrases for checking in and staying at Japanese accommodations.</p>
   
    <img src="/assets/images/hotel.jpg" alt="At the Hotel" class="hero-img">

<div class="audio-player">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-play" style="font-size:30px;color:var(--shu)"></i>
  <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;">Listen to the pronunciation</strong>
    <audio controls src="/assets/audio/hotel.mp4" style="width: 100%;"></audio>
  </div>
</div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Example Dialogue</h2>
    <div class="dialogue-box">
      <div class="line">
        <b>Traveler</b>
        <span class="ja">すみません。予約した裕貴（ひろたか）です。</span>
        <span class="ro">Sumimasen. Yoyaku shita Hirotaka desu.</span>
        <span class="en">Excuse me. I'm Hirotaka, I have a reservation.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="line">
        <b>Staff</b>
        <span class="ja">お待ちしておりました。パスポートをお願いします。</span>
        <span class="ro">Omachi shite orimashita. Pasupōto o onegaishimasu.</span>
        <span class="en">We have been expecting you. May I have your passport, please?</span>
      </div>
      <hr style="border:0; border-top:1px dashed #f1cbc6; margin:20px 0;">
      <div class="line">
        <b>Traveler</b>
        <span class="ja">Wi-Fiのパスワードは何ですか？</span>
        <span class="ro">Waifa-i no pasuwādo wa nan desu ka?</span>
        <span class="en">What is the Wi-Fi password?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="line">
        <b>Staff</b>
        <span class="ja">これです。朝食は７時からです。</span>
        <span class="ro">Kore desu. Chōshoku wa shichi-ji kara desu.</span>
        <span class="en">Here it is. Breakfast starts from 7:00.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Check Vocabulary</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 30px;">
